downloadDescription: Detailed character weight specifications for sorting and comparison of Unicode strings.
detailsSection: This document contains detailed character weight specifications that permit consistent sorting and comparison of Unicode strings.
systemRequirementsSection: The documentation is available in the Adobe Portable Document Format (PDF) which you can open using Adobe Reader, available at http://www.adobe.com.
installInstructionSection: The data in this document is not used by itself, but rather as one of the inputs to the comparison algorithm specified in [MS-ADTS] section 6.5. The layout and format of data in this file is also specified there.
